---
// src/components/content-conversion/PlatformReadyContent.astro
---
<section class="py-20 bg-brand-navy text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Prepared for Kajabi, LMS Platforms, and Course Websites</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Content conversion should end with assets that are easy to build into a platform. We organize your materials so they can be used inside Kajabi, LMS platforms, course websites, memberships, or internal training portals.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto backdrop-blur-sm">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-y-6 gap-x-8">
        {[
          "Course name",
          "Module names",
          "Lesson titles",
          "Lesson descriptions",
          "Video/script notes",
          "Downloads",
          "Quizzes",
          "Resource list",
          "Access notes",
          "Student support content",
          "Upload-ready folder structure"
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
             <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                 <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
             </div>
             <span class="text-gray-200 font-medium">{item}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 italic">
          Note: Platform setup is a separate service if the client also wants TheEduAssist to build the system.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
